snippet.title: PC Building Simulator 2 | Open Beta Available Now
snippet.description:
Join us in the PC Building Simulator 2 Open Beta (ends June 20th), and if you play it during this time you'll receive 15% off the full game at launch. 

Download now 👉 https://epic.gm/pcbs2
